TSX- and ASX-listed Champion Iron has appointed Michael Marcotte investor relations VP. Marcotte – a chartered financial analyst – previously spent 15 years working with resource equities for Macquarie Capital Markets Canada. Champion CEO Michael O’Keeffe said Marcotte joins the company at a crucial time in its growth cycle, with the Bloom Lake mine, in Quebec, in commercial production. “He will ensure an effective investor relations programme is implemented in the coming months.